    <Statements>
      <Statement>Understand that a function is a rule that assigns to each input exactly one output. The graph of a function is the set of ordered pairs consisting of an input and the corresponding output.&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt;</Statement>
    </Statements>
